  "title": "Outlet Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilites</strong></p>\n<p>- Restaurant daily operation</p>\n<p>- Assists the F&amp;B Cost Controller in Conducting month-end inventory of beverage supplies, operating   supplies, food supplies and operating equipment.</p>\n<p>- Selects, recruits, train and evaluates employees in his/her assigned outlet.</p>\n<p>- Ensure high quality of customer service</p>\n<p>- Prepares effective duty roster to ensure sufficiency of manpower in accordance to volume of business.</p>\n<p>- Administers personnel action, on leaves, overtime requests, disciplinary actions and commendation.</p>\n<p>- Performs other duties as assigned by Management.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>- Minimum of 2 to 3 years experience in F&amp;B- Good knowledge in the Food &amp; Beverage products and high-end service levels</p>\n<p>- Self motivated and able to work in a fast paced environment</p>\n<p>- Organized with strong planning, good communication and interpersonal skills</p>",
